{"tid":2223602,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"洛杉磯萬人動漫展堅持12月舉行 當局批評決定不成熟","createTime":"2020-09-30T03:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T06:24:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48e3893826148a6ca76a34c6265422cdb3a69502","tid":2223602,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）集合漫畫、科幻、遊戲和流行文化的「洛杉磯動漫展」（LA Comic Con）的主辦單位宣佈，將於12月如期舉行展覽，設入場人數限制、要求戴口罩等。但當地目前仍禁止舉行展覽，洛杉磯會議及旅遊局行政總監Doane Liu批評，主辦單位的決定不成熟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200930/4TEAASFD2ZAS7G3G3NU7PRTPPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200930%2F4TEAASFD2ZAS7G3G3NU7PRTPPI%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=163b49a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200930%2F4TEAASFD2ZAS7G3G3NU7PRTPPI%2F&h=c593d1d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200930/4TEAASFD2ZAS7G3G3NU7PRTPPI/</a>"},{"pid":"8f505886208ab4450e45ff3bc9aab9f902fbfc00","tid":2223602,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"今年真係應該忍一忍"},{"pid":"ac6ad29cbdc36a0a504237368e54474972027944","tid":2223602,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"我有去呀<br />\n幾無聊"},{"pid":"4864f1599333232a48ea9bd1981cd7e0470d86e6","tid":2223602,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ac6ad29cbdc36a0a504237368e54474972027944","tid":2223602,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"我有去呀<br />\n幾無聊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"巴打去完搭時光機返嚟？<br />\n12月支那同印度開戰未？"},{"pid":"43aecc99a56fe4ec4e6cab99f9b215089963d1db","tid":2223602,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"係咪9 成係ironman個d"},{"